The,TomTom,Online,Traffic,Flow,API,allows,developers,to,construct,web,based,and,mobile,apps,that,display,real,time,traffic,data,on,maps,It,is,powered,by,the,trademarked,TomTom,Traffic,portal,and,displays,real,time,data,of,prevailing,traffic,conditions,on,selected,roads,Users,can,use,different,zoom,levels,to,view,details,of,incidents,such,as,traffic,jams,and,delays,right,from,the,starting,point,to,the,destination,point,of,a,route,The,RESTful,API,sends,requests,in,HTTP,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,JSONP,or,XML,format